OL,5, The Taliban have excluded girls from   
OL,6, Afghan secondary schools, after they   
OL,7, ordered only boys and male teachers to 
OL,8, return to the classroom.               
OL,10,FA statement from the Islamist group    
OL,11,Fsaying secondary classes would resume  
OL,12,Fmade no mention of girls or women.     
OL,14,FOne Afghan schoolgirl told the BBC she 
OL,15,Fwas devastated. "Everything looks very 
OL,16,Fdark," she said.                       
OL,18,FDespite Taliban promises it is the     
OL,19,Flatest sign Afghanistan is returning to
OL,20,Fthe harsh rule of the 1990s.           
